## PART II: METHODOLOGY ARCHITECTURE

### 2.1 Core Principle: Trust Nothing, Verify Everything

**Problem discovered in this chat**: Documentation often claims features "work" without verification. AI can hallucinate completeness.

**Solution**: Every finding must have:
- **HYPOTHESIS**: What we believe
- **EVIDENCE**: File path, line number, commit hash
- **VERIFICATION**: How it was tested (ran code, screenshot, etc.)
- **ARTIFACT**: Written to disk, not just context

### 2.2 Core Principle: Parallel Extraction, Sequential Synthesis

**Phase 1**: Many agents extract in parallel (maximize coverage)
**Phase 2**: Fewer agents validate and cross-reference
**Phase 3**: Single synthesis produces final output

```
EXTRACTION (parallel)     VALIDATION (parallel)     SYNTHESIS (sequential)
    ‚îå‚îÄ Agent 1 ‚îÄ‚îê            ‚îå‚îÄ Agent A ‚îÄ‚îê              ‚îå‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îê
    ‚îú‚îÄ Agent 2 ‚îÄ‚î§            ‚îú‚îÄ Agent B ‚îÄ‚î§              ‚îÇ  SYNTHESIZER ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ Agent 3 ‚îÄ‚î§  ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ñ∫     ‚îú‚îÄ Agent C ‚îÄ‚î§  ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ñ∫       ‚îÇ   (single)   ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ Agent 4 ‚îÄ‚î§            ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò              ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò
    ‚îî‚îÄ ... N ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò
```

### 2.3 Core Principle: Disk-Based Memory

**Problem**: Context window is limited. Knowledge can be lost.

**Solution**: All findings written to `_migration_memory/` folder. Agents read/write artifacts, not just return reports.

### 2.4 Core Principle: Debate for Decisions

When multiple valid approaches exist, spawn agents with opposing perspectives:
- SIMPLICITY advocate
- COMPLETENESS advocate
- PERFORMANCE advocate
- SYNTHESIZER (produces consensus)

