## PART VI: AGENT ORCHESTRATION RULES

### 6.1 Resource Policy

**Tokens**: UNLIMITED. Use as many as needed for quality.
**Agents**: UNLIMITED. Parallelize aggressively.
**Time**: Not a constraint. Thoroughness over speed.

### 6.2 Artifact Persistence

ALL agent outputs go to disk:
```
_migration_memory/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 00_TERRITORY_MAP.md
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 01_canvas.md
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 02_domain.md
