‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ...
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 20_math_validation.md
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ...
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 30_debate_simple.md
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 30_debate_complete.md
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 30_debate_perf.md
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 35_decisions.md
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ SYNTHESIS_NOTES.md
```

### 6.3 Quality Over Economy

**DO**: Run 20 agents if it improves coverage
**DO**: Re-run phases if results are incomplete
**DO**: Spawn additional agents for edge cases
**DON'T**: Skip verification to save tokens
**DON'T**: Assume documentation is accurate
**DON'T**: Rush to synthesis before extraction is complete

### 6.4 Verification Protocol

For any claim marked "VERIFIED":
- Code was actually run, OR
- Test was actually executed, OR
- Screenshot was actually captured
- File:line evidence provided

For any claim marked "CLAIMED":
- Documentation says it works
- No actual verification performed
- Should be verified before relying on it

